com.example.wikiaudio.wikipedia

Class Wikipedia

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.wikiaudio.wikipedia.Wikipedia

  • public class Wikipedia
extends java.lang.Object
    Facade singleton class to all interaction with wikipedia. Main purpose is to manage requests to wikipedia and decide what is the best method thread/AsyncTask/workManager.

    • Method Detail

      • searchForPage

        public void searchForPage(java.lang.String pageName,
                          java.util.List<PageAttributes> attributes,
                          java.util.List<Wikipage> listToFill,
                          WorkerListener workerListener)
        Search a name for relevant wiki pages. Fills list to fill with relevant wiki pages with name and id data. Does not handle bad writing. (if you now the exact name of the page you want use `getPage()` ).
        Parameters:
        pageName - the value to search.
        attributes - currently not in use. can be null.
        listToFill - the list to fill with result.
        workerListener - what to do if task fails or is successful.

      • getPagesNearby

        public void getPagesNearby(double latitude,
                           double longitude,
                           int radius,
                           java.util.List<Wikipage> listToFill,
                           java.util.List<PageAttributes> pageAttributes,
                           WorkerListener workerListener)
        gets Wikipages nearby the given coordinates. if successful, fills the 'listToFill' with found pages. And then runs workerListener.
        Parameters:
        latitude - the latitude to preform the search on.
        longitude - the longitude to preform the search on.
        radius - the radius from coordinates to search in.
        listToFill - the Wikipage list to be filled with results.
        pageAttributes - the attributes to get on each wiki page found.
        workerListener - what to do if task fails or is successful.

      • getWikipagesByName

        public void getWikipagesByName(java.util.List<java.lang.String> names,
                               java.util.List<PageAttributes> pageAttributes,
                               java.util.List<Wikipage> listToFill,
                               WorkerListener workerListener)
        get a list of wikipages by name. notice! onSuccess runs after all process is finished. onFailure runs each time bringing one of the pages failed.
        Parameters:
        names - the names of the wikipages to bring.
        pageAttributes - the attributes to get on each page.
        listToFill - the list to fill with the results.
        workerListener - callback when finished.
